notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-07T07:27:25.206Z",maintainer-agent,"Planning pass 2026-07-07: candidate additional derived signal — estimation calibration. estimated_minutes is a required metadata field but nothing compares it against actual duration derived from history streams (claim-to-close spans, cf. pm-pee5 flow metrics). Two uses: (a) ranking — items whose elapsed active time greatly exceeds estimate are aging-WIP risks worth surfacing; (b) planning — a per-author/per-type calibration factor makes future estimates and pm plan step budgeting evidence-based. Derivation belongs in this feature store; presentation belongs in pm-pee5."
